INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('107', 'They made the course harder on purpose in spring because it was so much easier than the one in fall; excellent professor; quiz and problem set every week; material is easy if you go to the lectures ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('107', 'Pretty easy class, but weekly problem sets can get hard and stressful. He''s pretty lax on grading and so a lot of things are dropped in the class. Would highly recommend because you learn a decent amount without putting in crazy amounts of work. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('108', 'Willis is not as renown and good as Noor but still decent. He is a very enthusiastic man but his notes are average. Furthermore, his exam questions are a little misleading; however, he generally makes easier exams than Noor but there are very little room for error in these exams (1 question wrong means 1% off in final grade and there is no curve). Lastly, bio 202 is one of the easier classes for a Pratt student to take if he/she is looking to fulfill a NS or bio requirement. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('108', 'light workload, easy A, professor is nice but not very organized ' );
