INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('130', 'WOW this class is very very very time consuming, and the content can be extremely hard. We have assignment, 3-hour stats or 3-hour lab and quiz every single week. There are 3 exams, 3-4 lab reports and 1 mini project this semester. Professor Henriquez is very approachable, and replies to piazza questions very quickly. This class is required for BME students, but it is also VERY rewarding (you will definitely learn a lot). ' );
