INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('225', 'Recommend the class. Completely managable. Class is relatively easy up until the first midterm if you''ve had any CS or previous programming experience (including AP Computer Science). The second half the class gets more difficult, and there are much more programming assignments. These can be incredibly time consuming, but completely doable. Be sure to pick good partners towards the end of the semster so you aren''t swamped with all the work. UTAs and TAs will be your best friends if you need help. There are also frequent tutoring/help sessions where TAs are just sitting in the Link. There is no huge curve or anything in the class (maybe a very small minor one), and the exams are very fair. ' );
