INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('283', 'Highly recommended. Go through problem sets and ways to solve them (and code them up). Great to build up your compsci-way of thinking. Fall semester will involve in participating in ICPC-ACM - a world-wide coding competition. Some ppl are very serious about it. Don''t need to enroll - most ppl actually just go, do problems and prepare for the competition ' );
