INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('320', 'In groups of three build an application for a real outside client in the semester. Less about hard-core programming compared to 308, but more about understanding the need of the client (translating that into technical terms), documentaing, and executing to satisfy the need. Great mimic of the real world programming if you want a taste of that ' );
