INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('375', 'Great freshmen seminar! Almost no readings and homework were all about taking photos. I took this as my first photography course ever with my first DSLR and now you can see my works here: https://500px.com/lanlyjin p.s. You can rent DSLR for free from the center of Documentary Study so you do not have to buy one unless you really want to. ' );
