INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('380', 'Heavy workload with weekly homework and almost weekly long lab reports which were pretty pointless. As a ECE major requirement class, it was basic and if you did homework and listened in class should be totally fine. Building the robot was pretty fun however if you got a partner with no programming skills life would really suck. A lot of late nights at the Teer lab. Take this class with Gustafson, he is the best one. ' );
