INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('399', 'EXTREMELY HEAVY WORKLOAD. Be prepared to be bombarded with multiple homework assignments, hour-long labs, and various reports weekly. It could be fun if you are only taking this ONE class the entire semester. Introduces several important concepts in digital designs including multiplier/divisor, fast adders, asynchronous design, etc. Seriously challenging. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('400', 'Hardware version of ECE/CS 250. Build a processor (with verilog) through the semester. Work load is not crazy but still takes a decent amount of time. Contents are reasonable to understand so don''t need to worry about too much. Very rewarding, and since it''s needed for ECE so just go for it. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('401', 'The lecturer is extremely horrible and unclear at teaching. Furthermore, he lets the head TA write homeworks, exams and hand out arbitrary grades. In conclusion, do not take the class with Professor Chen, he does not care about his students at all and is mainly concerned with research. ' );
