INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('707', 'Workload alert - if you started learning French with French 101 at Duke (like me), you are likely to struggle a bit with writing and this class will take a lot of time. But if you enjoy writing, you''ll have lots of fun with the class materials as well. Essay/quiz/project every week. Class participation is extremely important and strictly graded. Professor is great and very approachable. ' );
