INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('749', 'Terrible class, dry subject, very poor teaching, not difficult but far too many assignments. Would not recommend ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('750', 'While Sloan is incredible knowledgable and happy to help you one-on-one, he expects you to be independent in your learning ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('751', 'This is an amazing class and prob the best class i''ve taken at duke. Prof Liz is absolutely brilliant. Everything she said in the class is so eloquent and profound, making me want to write down every word she said. She''s a philosopher by training, so she sometimes goes very deep, leaving the class perplexed. She gives you very high-level reading and helps the class to analyzed almost word by word. The class is like two essays, but I spent 30+ hrs on a 6-8 pg essay and prob a lot more on the final 10-12 pg essay. This class is the women''s studies gateway, laying out the theoretical foundation. I highly recommend everyone to take this class. ' );
