INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1043', 'Class grade is based on rank order (top 20% = A). Most of your grade will come from you and your group running a business simulation that competes against the other teams in the class. Grody is pretty fun and knows a lot about how business works, but not an easy A course. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1044', 'Project based class. Future entrepenurs should take this class. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1045', 'Take it if you like sports. Project and paper based class. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1046', 'Great professor, extremely sweet and explains concepts clearly. Expects you to practice though. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1047', 'Great prof and light workload. If you don''t mind paying more, I''d recommend the one-on-one section (MUSIC 208) which would make you improve much faster. Sometimes listening to her commenting on others'' singing could be helpful too though! ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1048', 'Designed for ppl with no background in Guitar. Would have to spend some time to practice the basic skills but class in general is very chill. If you know other instruments/musical notations/basic music theory could help a lot ' );
