INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1071', 'This class is about music from 1000 years ago, mostly church music. First section of music history and mandatory for music major students ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1072', '- covering music in Baroque period - no assignment but difficult quizzes and exams - strict professor with harsh comments ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1073', 'Little work in this class. Graded based on a few papers and listening quizzes. Professor Todd is a world renowned scholar on Mendelssohn. Highly recommend. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1074', 'Not a fun class if you just wanted to learn some music knowledge for fun. A lot of work. The listening quiz was pain. The grading was pretty harsh and expectation is high on those music critiques written assignment. That being said, Todd is extremely knowledgable and he is a genius if you want to learn more about European post-Classical music and opera. ' );
