INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1269', 'It is a lot to memorize. A lot of people say its an easy A, but you will get A only if you are good at memorizing stuff. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1270', 'Had two midterms and a final. Easy materials but a lot to memorize. Lab every week, participation based. Harsh grading. No homework. Three research participation required but super easy. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1270', 'DON''T TAKE THE CLASS WITH PROFESSOR VIETH. Her exams are so tricky. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1271', 'Angela Vieth is so far my favorite psychology professor. She is very nice and personable, always happy to help you out. The workload is very low. There is no homework at all. Tests might be tricky but as long as you do the reading and go to lectures, it''s an easy A ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1271', 'Excellent professor. Light workload. But you need to memorize lots of stuff before exam. The exam is relatively easy if you memorize everything. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1272', 'Professor is really organized and nice. if you read through materials carefully and work before the exam, it’s not tough to get an A. But not an easy A class. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1273', 'Great intro class; 2 midterms 1 final; muiltiple choices and essays; a lot of memorization ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1274', 'she''s a great lecturer. Basically memorization based course… ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1275', 'Super interesting and easy class. Not much commitment but you actually learn a lot of things that are relevant. Strongly recommend. Also Jorgi is adorable and hilarious. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1276', 'Muphy''s tests are open-book and open-internet, but it''s not easy since most of the content in the exams are neither in the book nor can be googled (mostly what she said in the class). Also, it may not be easy to get a good grade in assignments and participation (depends on the TA). ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1277', 'The lectures are fun and the course material is very interesting. Dr. Murphy likes the application of the ideas and her tests are online - open book and open friends! But the questions can be tricky sometimes.. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1278', 'Great professor, very easy concepts and exams. Though you''ll have to pay for an online ebook and do end-of-chapter quiz every week. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1279', 'Not too bad, lots of reading, interesting material ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1280', '3 exam class with discussion session ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1281', 'Show up to class, that’s it. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1282', 'Pretty easy class, slides are pretty much sum up all the book materials. Exams are all multiple choice. Not much work required as long as one keeps up with the work. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1283', 'Two multiple choice midterms; require details from the text and her class; if you know the materials, the midterms are not hard, except for a few tricky questions. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1284', 'A very interesting class. I love it. Don''t miss lecture ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1285', 'Professor Wilbourn is very very knowledgeable and passionate about what she studies and you defenitely learn a lot from this class, things that can be applied to the real world.Lectures are engaging. Grading is fair. For the exams you need to remember a lot of details from lecture/textbook.Put efforts then you will get a good grade ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1286', 'Dr. Tomasello is arguably the most famous psych professor here; however, this clas is pretty boring; two midterms all MCs; have to pay attention and take notes in class ' );
