INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1308', 'Easy class. The professor is super nice and conducts global health research ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1309', 'Super easy class for college requirement. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1310', 'Nice professor and easy materials, topic is very interesting and I suppose it is an easy A class ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1311', 'Three midterms; three reaction papers; one final paper; Professor is nice and organized, but a decent amount of work ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1312', 'Reasonable workload, fair test, lecture is really engaging and inspiring! Textbook reading is a must. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1313', 'Readings every week. Was not that difficult and was pretty interesting. Papers were ok. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1314', '300-word reading responses every class, which can get a bit annoying at times. Workload is reasonable. Material is interesting - half science half humanities. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1315', 'a lot of workload, but learns a lot about social development ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1316', 'nice prof easy class. There are class projects, service learning and midterm and final ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1317', '18 hours of community service work, but pretty easy and interesting class ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1318', 'Strongly recommend! Lectures are fun and readings are easy. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1319', 'Dr. Hare is amazing. He is a hilarious person and his class is always so much fun. You can learn a lot of interesting stuff about cognitive evolution from this class. Definitely recommended. However, there is a lot of reading and this is not an easy A class if you do not finish the reading on time. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1320', 'Taught by a professor of psychology and a professor of philosophy, this course is interesting but soooo hard. So many tough readings to do. Final Paper + Final Exam. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1321', '2 projects (one 10-pager and one presentation), a final paper (12-15 pages), and five 1.5-2 pages thought pieces. Overall an interesting class but nothing in particular. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1322', 'Really easy class; daily assignment that is easy to complete, and if you submit everything you get an A ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1323', 'She''s pretty unorganized as a professor; two midterms and one final project; midterms have some really detailed notes from class, but it''s somewhat difficult to follow her in class because she speaks at an extremely low volume ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1324', 'I don''t think the work load is heavy. The professor is great, definitely take with him, as he is humorous and keeps you entertained. Grading is on the harsh side, as this is one of the core classes for public policy major. Very interesting class with little work load, definitely one of the best classes I''ve had at Duke ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1325', 'Interesting and chill class for Psych majors and non-majors alike. Midterms, short paper/project, and a final paper, no final exam. Grading was easy and don''t take attendance. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1326', 'Very approachable professor. One midterm, one final. They are non-cumulative and relatively easy. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1326', 'The topics are interesting. There is one midterm, one assignment (3-5 pages), one long essay, one final. The professor is very nice ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1327', 'Weekly short essays;, one group presentation, one final paper; easy class ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1328', 'This course is the most beneficial psychology course for me personally. Practicing and studying mindfulness totally changed me. I had less stress and better sleep quality. The workload is very balanced and professor is chill. Highly recommend. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1329', 'Little workload and the material is really interesting. We did a mock jury for a real Durham homicide case and went to watch the final appeal 15 years after the conviction where the person finally walked out of jail. The professor is a bit OCD, but on the bright side the class is really organized. 2-3 short papers and that''s it for grading in the semester. Even if you''re not a psych major, this class talks about law, medicine, and performing art (dancing, martial arts, etc.) that even non-psych majors could enjoy! ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1330', 'HEAVY WORK LOAD NICE PROFESSOR. YOU ARE ABLE TO LEARN WRITING ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1331', 'Very useful materials pertaining to college career and life in general! Work load is a bit heavy but as long as you show effort, Thompson will reward you with good grade. Definitely recommend! ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1332', 'Readings are recommended but you can skip. Workload is basically one problem set a week and three memos a semester. It is a fairly easy class but don''t expect it to boost your GPA ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1333', 'Easy class, materials are useful in future pubpol/polisci studies; lectures are boring and not too helpful but some TAs are great ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1334', 'Very interesting course which gives an overview of all the important theories in the field of public policy (game theory, cost and benefit analysis, decision analysis, political analysis...) Professor Vigdor is the best you can get for 155, though she does not teach at Duke anymore. Not so much work but grading rather harsh, be prepared. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1335', 'Extremely dull class for most people. If you''re interested in public policy, do NOT take this class first as it is not representative of what the rest of the major will be. Take electives first to get a real feel for the major and just power through this class. Worst class of the major, in my opinion. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1336', 'Great class and great professor. Sometimes heavy reading, but overall reasonable workload. Lectures are useful, midterms are easy, but memos can be challenging ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1336', 'Intro core for public policy majors. Mayer is a good professor and an experienced policy analyst. Memo grading is pretty harsh, but the midterms and finals are relatively easy and managable. Take advantage of extra credit oppoturnities! ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1337', 'Awesome professor. The tests are easy but memos are harshly graded. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1338', 'I really like professor Bermeo and enjoyed the class a lot! The thing about this class, as you might have already hear, is that the grading system can be frustrating because everything is graded by TAS and the memos can be subjective. Also, the curve for this class is really harsh. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1339', 'You have to take this class if you want to major in Pubpol. It''s hard to get a good grade in this class, but I learned a lot. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1339', 'Class- material is not hard at all and some basic knowledge in Econ would help. HOWEVER, they grade memos really hard. Prof- good and passionate, but doesn’t give instructions on memos ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1340', 'This is an very interesting course. Demanding, but not impossible. Memo writing can be challenging but the exams are easy. The instructor is very clear and organized. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1341', 'It will be a hard class if you don''t enjoy the topic. The professor is knowledgable and nice. Overall, I liked the class. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1342', 'Very senior-heavy. ( Public speaking skills are something that can benefit you a lot in the long run if you are good at it) Very insightful and considerate professor. We basically watched some of the most awesome speeches on TED, university commencement address and etc and learned from them. We were asked to give improv speeches and get feedback from all the classmates. Very little homework but you need to be willling to be active and speak out in class. I took this class with Jahil Okafor and Quinn Cook, which was pretty cool. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1343', 'Amazing course. Good luck getting in since hundreds of people try to get in every semester. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1343', 'Well-intentioned but ignorant professor who creates a Kitsch-like environment where students are literally crying during the final class. Besides some confidence-nudging here and there, no actual technicals on public speaking are taught. Incredibly arbitrary grading only dependent on final portfolio, but relatively lenient if you express good intentions and contribute in class. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1344', 'FOCUS class. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1345', 'Class- the book is dense, tests could be hard. Prof- knowledgeable ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1346', 'Super easy class. only one midterm and meet once a week ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1347', 'A little disorganized and random - you learn everything and anything about Russia from ethnic groups to Soviet economic systems to language and identity to music culture to higher education. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1348', 'Light discussion-based course. You don''t really have to do the readings because discussions digress a lot and tend to be general/philosophical. There are 3 papers + a final research paper. Grading is fair. Newcity is one of the most nonpartisan professors I''ve ever had who genuinely embraced diverse viewpoints. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1349', 'Very challenging but worth it. Read 300 pages each week plus a 500 word essay every week. Great choice if you want to step out of your comfort zone. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1350', 'Awesome course if you are looking for a pub pol history elective. Very thought provoking course material and great class discussions ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1351', 'A lot of readings! I''m really interested in 20th century history, so I enjoyed the readings. Good class if you like the topic. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1352', 'Prof is witty, accessible, and very intelligent. Inspiring. Explains how to view service and poverty differently. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1353', 'Easiness: This is a very easy class with one midterm, two papers, and a couple service project components. There are a couple quizzes scattered in between but if you feel like you’re not doing well or don’t know the material well, you can choose to ball up the quiz, and toss it, but then submit a paper within 24 hours. Workload: There are weekly readings. That is it. And the occasional paper. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1354', '2 assessments and 1 research paper; need to participate in class ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1355', 'The professor was very enthusiastic about the topic. I guess it''s a hit or miss. Our class had a great time with her and (I think) everyone got a pretty good grade. She even cancelled the final. We went to volunteer at a food bank instead. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1356', 'Weekly readings, two papers and two times leading class discussions. A lot of (interesting) readings. Very relevant and enriching materials but tests are subjective to the professor''s opinions. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1357', 'Solid amount of reading and work, very conceptual things that require a lot of synthesis. Professor is top-notch, extremely knowledgeable and very good at conveying the material. Don''t expect it to be easy though. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1358', 'Core course for pubpol majors. Rose is a wonderful professor, though readings are often not so relevant. One in-class midterm. Four memos. One final. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1359', 'Carnes is absolutely one of the best professors I have ever had at Duke. TAKE PUBPOL 301 WITH CARNES! ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1360', 'Highly recommend this professor. Her classes are fun and engaging. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1361', 'If you''re interested in US politics, this is a great introductory class. Professor is not the greatest teacher, but very willing to help you ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1362', 'Carnes is very charismatic. Course material is very structured and he TRULY wants you to succeed. But all the group activities are kind of nonsense. Recommend taking 301 with him. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1362', 'Light workload, practical materials for understanding policy making, lenient grader, awesome guest lecturers ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1363', '4 memos and 1 midterm per semester. Professor is chill and engaging ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1364', 'Weekly quiz, professors are cool ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1365', 'Don''t do it with him if you care about your GPA. You definitely learn a lot in the class, but his daily quizzes on the readings are based purely on HIS interpretation of the thing. Challenges not welcomed. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1366', 'No exam but semester long op-ed project. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1367', 'Charney is a very interesting person and could be opinionated. The trick to get a good grade is to have a very particular mindset that caters to Charney''s. Not a lot of work, and the class is interesting. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1368', 'I don''t think the work load is heavy. The professor is great, definitely take with him, as he is humorous and keeps you entertained. Grading is on the harsh side, as this is one of the core classes for public policy major. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1368', 'Charney is the bomb. Take this class whether or not you are Pubpol ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1369', 'Professor Charney is great, really learnt a lot. Though the reading quizzes can be a little annoying ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1370', 'It''s a lot of material, weekly quizzes and group assignments but you learn enormous amount of ethics/philosophy. Charney is leaving Duke after 2019 Spring through. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1371', 'Brilliant professor, but not an easy grader. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1372', 'Love the readings. Love the course. Love the professor. Discussed interesting concepts from Kant to utilitarianism to Machiavelli. Participation is a must. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1373', 'I loved this class. We had many engaged and interesting discussions in class. Take this core with this professor. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1374', 'This class was a mess. Hamoudi is nice though, and great in office hours ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1375', '3 exams with weekly problem sets. Overall: good teacher and good class. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1376', 'one of the core courses for pub pol majors, definitely easier than Econ 201, Seth can confuse himself with material sometime, but the grading is relatively lenient ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1377', 'It''s a requirement course for pub pol -- can''t avoid it. Workload is okay. Material sort of interesting. Professor - okayish. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1378', 'Do not take a course with Coffey. He has no idea what he''s doing. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1379', 'prof is nice but boring. 1 mid term 1final but many assignments ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1379', 'Less than 5hours per week, reading is helpful but not necessary, low pace lecture ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1380', 'As a small class, this class had incredible discussions and Katzenstein asks great provocative questions. Lots of writing. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1381', 'Duke in France EDUCO course, count as pubpol elective. Basically no workload. exams are pure memorization ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1382', 'Class participation is expected. Readings tend to be long, and there are weekly blog posts. However, this would depened on the professor that''s teaching. It is not a difficult class per se, but meeting once a week for more than two hours means you better be interested in the topic. It is about U.S. national security. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1383', 'Summer course, we watched documentary films in class and write response paper at home. You can skim the reading. One 1000-word film analysis and one 2500 final paper. Easy grader. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1384', 'The University Course. We have guest speaker giving talks every week in a big lecture style. There''s also small group discussion session right after each lecture session. Highly recommend it ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1384', 'It is an university course so it is hard to get in. The topin is extremely interesting and we have guest speakers every week. Three papers total and anotated questions every week from the readings. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1385', 'Basically no workload but his instruction is unclear ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1386', 'It is a required class for public policy honors thesis. The class itself is really easy as long as you meet the deadlines for assignments. The hard part about this class is to stay motivated to work on the thesis continuously. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1387', 'Required for doing pub pol honor thesis. Pretty chill and open-ended, lots of autonomy. Rogerson is a great guy! ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1388', 'doesn''t meet often, you don''t have to do the reading, but a good way to keep you on track when writing thesis ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1389', 'HEAVY workload. Moderate difficulty, professor is a really good conversation facilitator. Material not super super interesting but okay ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1390', 'The biweekly assignment can be time consuming, leading is necessary, easy grading ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1391', 'Easy yet interesting course materials. Highly recommended. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1391', 'Nice professor; topics are interesting if you like Buddhism or gender topics; two papers and ten 300-word reading responses ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1392', 'The professor is kind of laid back and not really knowing what she is talking about. But she is a really nice person and you''ll get good grades if there''s more interaction with her. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1393', 'Lilliana is a little disorganized through the semester and her readings are a little bit too much to comprehend. But in fact you just need to skim through the readings and bring your personal opinions to class and that''s totally fine. She is really chill and gives good grades to everyone. I like her too:) ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1394', 'Best professor. Really cares about us. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1395', '80 pages of academic papers per week. Chill class with EI and W code but not writing component. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1396', 'Pretty chill Professor, easy A ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1397', 'The professor is really nice. She gives out lectures and writes her bullet points on the whiteboard each class. All you have to do is take notes based on her lecture and review your notes before exams. Grade based on 2 individual papers (4-5 pages), 1 group project, a midterm and a final exam. Easy class. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1398', 'Not too much work, asides from the LEAPS component of the class, which requires two hours of community service at a local retirement home each week. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1399', '1 reading assignment each week + 1 final paper + 1 group presentation + 4 tests. Although it seems a lot, the professor''s grading is pretty lenient and are mostly graded on a completion base. This class introduces the health disparities especially in the US, concerning different aspects including gender, race, LGBTQ, immigration, medicalization, doctor-patient relationship, etc. Would be a great class for pre-health people to be more aware of different psychosocial factors influencing health and what efforts physicians should make for better health care. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1400', 'Don''t take this class unless you need it for MMS. It''s a fairly easy class, but it''s boring and not very useful. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1401', 'Interesting topics; nice professor. Quizzes are challenging if you don''t pay attention to lectures; three team projects take some time. Grades are evenly distributed among different team projects, quizzes, and one mid-term individual paper ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1402', 'You need to go to class and take notes. One debate, one presentation, 4 quizes, two essays and one final paper. Prof gives a lot of extra credits. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1403', 'Easy grading. Be prepared to write and read a lot. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1403', 'Class is completely reading based. There can be a lot of readings sometimes but tests are easy and open ended even though they are also reading based. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1404', 'You know you have to take this class after reading the name of the class. I strongly recommend this class! It''s easy and you will learn a lot! 4 papers, but she often replace a few paper with other assignments (which are really easy) ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1405', '4 group papers based on reading/common sense/bs and you are done. So EZ and also have a lot of codes. I don''t know why this course exists, it''s like a cheat ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1405', 'easy A. four essays. no final. enough said. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1406', 'Boring class! Don''t take it with this professor. I heard this class is not bad with other teachers. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1407', 'We had two midterms and one final. The exams are not hard as long as you study the vocabulary and grammar. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1408', 'Very nice professor, but extremely unorganized. Interesting topics, but easily sidetracked. Discussion-based class. Doing the reading helps, but is not 100% necessary. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1409', 'We had two midterms and one final. The exams are not hard as long as you study the vocabulary and grammar. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1409', 'The class isn''t particularly difficult, but there is a lot of busy work. Some assignments are confusing a first, but there''s always a grading rubric available. The hardest part of exams is the vocab section , since there are so many vocab words in the chapter but no word bank. The professor is nice, but can be a hard grader on essays. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1410', 'Super easy class. Occasional textbook based homework, some small oral projects, some short writing assignments. Not sure if learned much with this prof though. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1411', 'Workload was relatively ok and the material wasn’t too hard. Course itself had challenging aspects but was doable. I thought the class was a good one for practicing Spanish in a classroom setting. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1412', 'Overall, I really enjoyed this class because the quality of instruction from the professor was very good. Since I haven’t taken a Spanish course since sophomore year of high school, this course was a good way to review a lot of the concepts I had forgotten, but I also learned many new grammatical rules and vocabulary. Generally, there was a medium amount of workload, since learning a language involves a constant practice of the ideas learned. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1413', 'Since the focus of this course is writing, we have written several essays and done a lot of work on short writing assignments. The professor is extremely patient and genuinely wants to help us develop our writing skills in Spanish in order to improve our ability to create strong arguments and support them. Overall, the course load isn’t too heavy, and we mainly just have to do big projects over a long period of time. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1414', 'easy ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1415', 'quite a lot of work invovled in the class, but the lectures and work are deisgned to help you best learn the material…need to put in effort to study though ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1416', 'If you want to take stat 101, I strongly recommend you to take with this professor. She''s nice, knowledgable and funny. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1417', 'Easy class. Professor is extremely energetic & enthusiastic, very willing to help. But if her brother Eric Lock substitutes (more likely now that she has infant twins), don''t bother paying attention. He''s an awful lecturer. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1418', 'The class is not hard but it comes with labs, homework, and projects. The assignments keep you busy. Dr. Mukherjee is very flexible and nice. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1419', 'The material is not hard, but there were just way to many tedious tasks. It''s also team-based and you need to finish lab as a team every week. Lectures were not bad. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1420', 'professor barely teaches anything in class because it is ''team-based learning''. However there''s no supplemental reading materials so you have to google everything. Basically self-teach yourself online for this class but lectures are mandatory. Grading is quite arbitrary as the professor omits some but not of the quizzes and decide the grades on a whim. 0/10 recommend this class as you''ll be confused for most of the time wondering what is going on and what you are supposed to do for this class. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1421', '100% recommend because Banks is a great person to get to know ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1422', 'Difficulty- Hard but Easy A. Works and materials covered were actually pretty hard, but in the end he gave everyone an A. (some people got curve down from A+ to A) The professor is actually a genius. He read like over 8000 books in his life ( And remember the details of many of them.) ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1423', 'Workload is not heavy. The difficulty level is easy. Professor is great! ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1424', 'There''s a quiz every class. Weekly graded homework, four midterms, weekly lab (very easy), no final. Heavy workload, but you learn a lot. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1425', 'Relatively hard class and heavy workload. Materials are easy if you put in enough time and effort. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1426', 'Class- daily quiz and exams are hard. Prof- Banks is an amazing professor but this class is just hard. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1427', 'Banks is so great! The most passionate professor I met! He knows everything related to statistics and could give real-life examples whenever you need. He remembers everyone''s name (about 100 students in his class every semester) and he makes sure you understand the material. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1428', 'We had four tests but no final. Quiz every lecture and a 7 hour/week problem set each week. Lab every week but easy. Learned a lot from this class though really tough material/grading and huge work load. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1428', 'Quiz every class. You have to go to office hour if you want to finish your homework. Exam is not too difficult, but the class moves very fast so make sure you don’t lag behind. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1429', 'This class requires a lot of time and effort. It''s curved but the curve is not very good. Be prepared to work on the hard problem sets every week and go to the office hours. The professor is damn smart. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1430', 'Banks is such a nice guy!!! he''s always willing to listen to you and even chat with you. but the course, as an intro level stats course, aims to cover too many topics that I feel we go into none of them deep enough. quiz in every class, and weekly homework. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1431', 'Great professor, very organized, explains questions clearly, a very comprehensive introduction to statistical methods and theories ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1431', 'Banks remembers everyone''s name and is super nice and kind! An intro course but you learn a lot, and the labs are easy but super helpful (your choice of Matlab or Stata). A is not hard if you do the practice quizzes & exams beforehand. Quizzes every lecture and exams every week, good transition from a Chinese way of learning : ) 3-7 hours per week, can vary. Recommend to STEM people: really useful! ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1432', 'Bloody hard. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1433', 'Pretty interesting. Learned useful R codes to do cool projects. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1434', 'Great professsor; good at explaining; class is 80% group work and 20% individual work; required to use R languages. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1434', 'Very very useful and insightful, a good combination of stats theory and coding. excellent professor. Medium workload. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1435', 'The class is very unstructured and the teacher expects you to know everything before class so she starts doing problem sets in class. Not really recommending it ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1436', 'Do your best to avoid this professor if you can... This course is really helpful in whatever you are studying. But the professor is ridiculously disorganized and her expectation is extremely unclear. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1437', 'This is a really fun class judging purely on the materials. You got to apply your knowledge to data analysis cases. However, the instructor is not very organized. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1438', 'Workload is fine, about 4-5 hours a week; tests are easy;attendance is not mandatory. Didn''t learn much besides coding in R. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1439', 'Not much work; boring ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1439', 'Weekly problem sets are graded harshly. Materials from the entire first half can be covered in a week. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1440', 'If you want to know what is like to be a stats major / do data science, take this course. This should be taken before STA230 if you haven''t made up your mind. The hw uses R and is really like what you will be doing in the future ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1441', 'Great prof. Hard to get used to at first without any bg in R. But Jerry''s extremely helpful. If you have to take the class, take it with him. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1441', 'The professor is very organized abou the class logistics and very clear abou the lecture. Useful class overall ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1441', 'Medium workload, homework required using R to analyze dataset and writing reports. Material was interesting and very useful in the real world. Reiter was an engaging and wonderful teacher so you just learn everything in class. Final project you got to choose your question and dataset and present the analysis on a poster. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1441', 'Professor very clear on course content and course expectation. Very useful course ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1442', 'Workload heavy, easy midterms ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1442', 'Worst class ever, taken out ur grade instantly ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1443', 'Nice professor, very willing to help. Reasonable workload and clear schedule ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1444', 'Stat core. Daniel is a REALLY nice guy, but his lectures are boring as hell. Grades should be ok if you put in some effort. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1445', 'Textbook is really helpful. Count toward both Math and Stats major requirement. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1446', 'The materials are quite difficult but the tests are easy ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1447', 'Covers the applications of the subject matter well. Homework is not excessive if done on time. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1447', 'Not a hard course, just go to each class and do the homework, you won''t have a bad grade. But I''ve heard this is a course that depends a lot of the professors. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1447', 'Difficulty - medium. Professor is very chill. I can just go up to him and say “yo whats up!” and he would be cool with it. Class is pretty easily graded. (Curved to A-) ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1448', 'The class is not focused on rigorous math proofs. Prof. Li used slides for this class, but some of the materials taught in class could not be found in the slides. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1449', 'Great professor. Very understanding and helpful. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1450', 'Interesting topic if you like stats. If you did well on problem set, then it should be easier for you. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1451', 'Professor is nice but is not good at teaching; workload is moderate but frequent assignment (nearly every week); choose other time slots of this course if it''s possible; they are much easier and don''t require much efforts ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1452', 'Learn alone but the best prof to take probability with ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1453', 'Prof is an interesting, quirky guy. Definitely a genius, hence the slight social awkwardness. Tests and homeworks can get quite hard, but not impossible to do (though I did spend 10 hours doing a take-home exam). Need to really understand the concepts in order to apply them to more complicated variations, so not for people who just want to get their stats req over with (it was definitely more focused on probability than stats) ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1454', 'The professor is interesting and smart. Very engaging, but the concepts are harder than I thought. A very useful class. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1455', 'Not recommending this professor. She basically reads and copies her notes, and isn''t very helpful in explaining the concept. Also assign coding assignment, which this class normally doesn''t require. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1456', 'Brilliant professor although a bit disorangized (he''s partially dyslexic). Office hours are a great resrouce. Problem sets are time consuming, but they''re extremely helpful. GO TO CLASS. He tries to give his students as many resources as possible to make the material easier. I learned a lot in his class, but if you get behind, it''s very difficult to catch up. Read the book (very good resource and required) if you feel lost and go to office hours! He''s a very fair and reasonable professor; he''ll make alternate assignments to help boost your grades or will take into consideration your problem sets, class attendance, etc. That being said, the material is pretty abstract and can get complicated. Unless you have to take this class, I would suggest not doing so and taking an easier stat class. It is supposed to be very difficult and geared towards math majors. I found the topics very interesting though, and I would say that I learned a lot. The professor is also very witty, brilliant, and entertaining. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1457', 'Funny and easy professor. Three equally weighted exams which were not very hard compared to other prof''s tests. Would recommend taking this with Professor Mela. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1458', 'useful class. Professor was ok. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1459', 'The exams are friendly - almost the same as the practice exam. The homework assignments are pretty hard, but the lowest grade can be dropped. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1459', 'Not hard ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1460', 'Easy A ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1461', 'Nice prof ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1462', 'Class notes are quite useful. The professor has a strong accent but is very nice. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1463', 'More math than stats. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1464', 'Very easy. Graphic calculators and cheat sheets are allowed. Use them wisely. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1464', 'Nice prof. Reachable and ppts are helpful. Take it with him if you can. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1464', 'GREAT PROF. TALKS IN CHINESE LOL AND YOU CAN ADD HIM ON WECHAT ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1464', 'My favorite Chinese professor (sadly he''s not teaching anymore). Very dry class but not that hard. Should be able to get a good grade with some effort ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1464', 'The class is curved to an A-. Nothing to worry about. Learn the powerpoint notes, and aim for perfection in homeworks. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1465', 'Easy homework, easy test ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1465', 'If you are taking Stats to fulfill major requirements, definitely take this class with Durrett. Straightforward tests and very fair grading. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1466', 'Supposedly an easy class with low workload. While the latter is true, Malen is not very good at explaining concepts, constantly makes mistakes when explaining questions in class and makes extremely diffcult and convoluted exams. Whatever you do, always remember to circle your final answers because Malen is constantly in a confused state of mind when grading exams. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1467', 'Prof has noticeable Indian accent, but is a super good lecturer, teaches you how to approach and solve problems. Weekly assignment counts for 40% of final grade so you need to put in some amount of work, and there could be lots of proofs. His midterms are more practical based, but also includes some proofs, definitely not an easy A. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1468', 'Easy ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1468', 'Super Easy! If you want to learn something, don''t go here! Go take Math 340! ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1469', 'DON''T TAKE IT WITH THIS PROF. Class is supposed to be easy but he''s terrible. Bad lecturer and not familiar with material himself. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1470', 'If you''d ever need to take Stats 230, take it with Mattingly. He''s super smart and funny (which makes the lectures an enjoyable experience.) Though he''s not really good at spelling or calculation, he is a great professor. The course itself is more challenging compared to what I''ve expected. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1471', 'The professor is strict. Late homework is marked zero. Class material is very easy and straight forward. Workload is light. ' );
INSERT INTO Comment VALUEs('1472', 'Such a lovely prof. Love the content ' );
